  "body": "### Description\r\nTracks the Merge Kintsugi implementation (November sprint): ref. reference: https://hackmd.io/@n0ble/kintsugi-spec\r\n\r\n- productize and move `merge-interop` branch to `master`\r\n\r\n  - [x] add merge spec datastructures #4503 \r\n  - [x] extend `TestSpecFactory` #4527\r\n  - [x] remove blind altair empty syncAggregate creation on block creation. (reference: https://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/pull/4503#discussion_r735744787) #4528\r\n  - [x] add Merge in `api.schema.merge` #4537\r\n  - [x] introduce a new way of running an entire set of UT against multiple Milestone #4563\r\n  - [x] introduce Merge in `teku.spec.logic` package\r\n    -  switch `SpecVersion::createMerge` to real Merge\r\n  - [ ] expand IT by implementing `GetBlockV2IntegrationTest::shouldGetMergeBlock`\r\n  - [x] #4593\r\n  - [x] implement merge specific reference test support (#4597)\r\n  - [x] #4641\r\n  - [x] #4659\r\n  - [x] #4668\r\n\r\n- implements specs 1.1.5 changes:\r\n\r\n  - [x] Add terminal block hash override ethereum/consensus-specs#2617\r\n  - [x] #4226 \r\n  - [x] #4670\r\n  - [x] Remove Union from ExecutionPayload transaction type ethereum/consensus-specs#2684\r\n  - [x] #4666\r\n  - [x] Add payload id as a return value to notify_forkchoice_updated ethereum/consensus-specs#2711\r\n  - [x] update penalty params for Merge ethereum/consensus-specs#2698\r\n\r\n - [ ] #4599  implement new [optimistic sync](https://hackmd.io/@n0ble/kintsugi-spec#Optimistic-sync) (additional ref: https://hackmd.io/Ic7VpkY3SkKGgYLg2p9pMg?view) #4599 \r\n- [x] #4716 \r\n\r\nnice to have:\r\n- [ ] submit a PR to [tuweni](https://github.com/apache/incubator-tuweni) to implement `Bytes4`, `Bytes8` and `Bytes20`\r\n- [x] #4667 introduce Merge state generator in `MockStartBeaconStateGenerator::createInitialBeaconState` by adding `ExecutionPayloadHeader` (note we've already done enough here to pass all reference tests)\r\n\r\nfar in the future:\r\n\r\n- [ ] remove default values and enforce validation in transition params (`SpecConfigBuilder::MergeBuilder::validate()`)\r\n- [ ] remove --X prefix and publish new params in documentation\r\n  - \"--Xee-endpoints\", \"--Xee-endpoint\" \r\n  - \"--Xvalidators-fee-recipient-address\"",
